OL,4,CFacebook: Our staff can carry on
OL,5,Cworking from home after Covid
OL,6, Facebook says its employees can
OL,7, continue working from home, even as
OL,8, other tech giants appear to be going
OL,9, off the idea.
OL,11,FThe social media company told the BBC
OL,12,Fit thinks remote work is "the future".
OL,14,FPeople in eligible roles at Facebook
OL,15,Fcan apply for permanent remote working,
OL,16,Fsubject to approval from managers.
OL,18,FSilicon Valley executives were quick to
OL,19,Fendorse the shift to remote work last
OL,20,Fyear, with some indicating it could
OL,21,Fcontinue even after the pandemic.
